data.description: Love the feel and finishes of new construction, but not the wait? Take a look at this nearly new beauty in Bellevue's Lions Gate neighborhood! Enjoy all the natural light w/ a wall of windows in the living room with stylish fireplace overlooking the large, fully fenced backyard. Kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances w/ gas range, quartz countertops, & hidden pantry.  At the back of the house, you will find a drop zone leading to the 3.5 car garage & an extra wide staircase taking you upstairs to the Primary bedroom which includes an en-suite bathroom w/ fully tiled walk-in shower & double sinks, and a large W/I closet. Plus, 3 additional bedrooms, 2 with W/I closets, a bathroom, and 2nd floor laundry room. Close to Offutt AFB & easy access to HWY 75. Don't miss your chance to see this amazing home! Schedule your showing today! AMA
